48	 * Authorization Matrix:
49	 * +------------------------------------+----------+----------+-------+----------+-----------+
50	 * | Endpoint                           | Unauthed | CUSTOMER | STAFF | SITE_MGR | ENT_ADMIN |
51	 * +------------------------------------+----------+----------+-------+----------+-----------+
52	 * | POST   /api/orders                 | 401      | 200      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
53	 * | GET    /api/orders/my              | 401      | 200      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
54	 * | GET    /api/orders/site/{siteId}   | 401      | 403      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
