57	 * | GET    /api/checkins/fraud-alerts  | 401      | 403      | 403   | 200      | 200       |
58	 * | POST   /api/tickets               | 401      | 200      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
59	 * | PATCH  /api/tickets/{id}/status   | 401      | 403      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
60	 * | POST   /api/ratings               | 401      | 200      | 200   | 200      | 200       |
61	 * | PATCH  /api/ratings/{id}/appeal/resolve | 401 | 403     | 403   | 200      | 200       |
62	 * | GET    /api/audit/range           | 401      | 403      | 403   | 403      | 200       |
63	 * | GET    /api/admin/incentive-rules | 401      | 403      | 403   | 403      | 200       |
